                    p.fs--1.mb-2.text-600 By Drik Smith ‚Ä¢ October 14, 2019
                    p.mb-0 You shouldn't need to read a review to see how nice and polished this theme is. So I'll tell you something you won't find in the demo. After the download I had a technical question, emailed the team and got a response right from the team CEO with helpful advice.
                    hr.my-4
